      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to be listing this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one\u2014the paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this perfect ride. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
