    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating the common fatigue points of the platform. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, offering unparalleled mechanical grip. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster with zero evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters remain firm and the interior trim is devoid of any delamination. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key specimen for the purist collector seeking the peak of the analog driving era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
